@ncw The beta build you just shared appears to work!
And yes we have `env_auth = true`.

Not sure if it will impact #5468 but as long as you defer to the AWS SDK for credentials things should keep working as expected

@tcasteix I've had same issue. To solve it I've had to add full access to my bucket:

```{
   "Version":"2012-10-17",
   "Statement":[
      {
         "Effect":"Allow",
         "Action": "s3:ListAllMyBuckets",
         "Resource":"*"
      },
      {
         "Effect":"Allow",
         "Action":"*",
         "Resource":"arn:aws:s3:::MY_BUCKET"
      },
      {
         "Effect":"Allow",
         "Action":"*",
         "Resource":"arn:aws:s3:::MY_BUCKET/*"
      }
   ]
}
```
